Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.53,0:00:02.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,This match...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.84,0:00:03.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,...is one we can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.56,0:00:08.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,I raise by 100 votes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:12.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oho!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:14.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.47,0:00:17.59,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's betting high to try to save her friend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.59,0:00:20.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even I didn't think things would go so perfectly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:22.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,I call.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:23.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,Call.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:24.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,Call.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:27.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gambling is a dull distraction.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.78,0:00:31.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The best way to make people do what you want is brute force.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:33.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right, Miyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:37.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,Everyone's bet 100 votes. Time to start playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:40.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,Round 2 begins now!
