Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:04.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}suki kirai suki kirai {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:08.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}Who will be first?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:08.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}saisho wa dare? {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:11.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}Moderation is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:11.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}hodohodo ja tsumannai {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:14.85,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}It's all or nothing.
