Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:21.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}Let's have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:21.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}tanoshimimashou {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:33.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}It feels good when you indulge.
