Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:48.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}We won't lose anything of importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:48.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}ushinau mono wa takaga shireteru {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:55.22,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}We may lose our tomorrow, but not our whole future.
