Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.40,0:24:12.22,Default2,,0,0,0,,What does singing mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.22,0:24:14.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,This is simply exquisite!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.47,0:24:17.46,Default2,,0,0,0,,Things have finally gotten interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.97,0:24:19.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,Let's have some fun.
